OL,3,CJersey's Les Amis choir 'sing in' the
OL,4,Cstart of Christmas
OL,6,FJersey's Les Amis choir marked the
OL,7,Fstart of Christmas with a festive
OL,8,Fcarol concert at Town Church in St
OL,9,FHelier on Wednesday 11 December.
OL,11,FThe choir was formed of service users
OL,12,Ffrom Les Amis, a charity that supports
OL,13,Fand empowers islanders with learning
OL,14,Fdisabilities and associated conditions.
OL,16,FThey provide residential, domiciliary,
OL,17,Fand respite care to around 100 people
OL,18,Fon the island.
