OL,3,CJersey's Les Amis choir 'sing in' the
OL,4,Cstart of Christmas
OL,6,FTheir annual concert brings some of
OL,7,Ftheir most musical service users
OL,8,Ftogether to celebrate how Christmas,
OL,9,Ffriendship, and music can bring people
OL,10,Ftogether.
OL,12,FLeslie Norman, chairman of Les Amis,
OL,13,Fsays he doesn't feel the festive
OL,14,Fseason has begun until the event takes
OL,15,Fplace.
OL,17,FHe says: "The most important thing
OL,18,Fabout today is the residents enjoying
OL,19,Fthemselves and expressing what
OL,20,FChristmas is all about.
