OL,3,CJersey's Les Amis choir 'sing in' the
OL,4,Cstart of Christmas
OL,6,F"If you look at their smiling faces,
OL,7,Fthe joy of their singing, and their
OL,8,Fjumping about - it's really the start
OL,9,Fof Christmas.
OL,11,F"The governor once said to me that
OL,12,F'until we have this concert, Christmas
OL,13,Fhasn't begun' - it's all just such
OL,14,Ffun."
OL,16,FKate Foley, Les Amis' Registered
OL,17,FManager, adds it's a joy to watch
OL,18,Fservice users find a connection with
OL,19,Fthe music through their participation
OL,20,Fin the choir.
