OL,3,CJersey's Les Amis choir 'sing in' the
OL,4,Cstart of Christmas
OL,6,FThe group also allows friendships to
OL,7,Fflourish and teaches skills such as
OL,8,FMakaton: a version of sign language.
OL,10,FShe says: "We've been practising since
OL,11,FSeptember and it's paid off massively.
OL,12,FThe effort and time that all the guys
OL,13,Fhave put into this has been amazing.
OL,15,F"It's just amazing to see them all
OL,16,Fcome together, enjoy themselves, and
OL,17,Fhave a big smile on their faces."
OL,19,FThe group will be performing eight
OL,20,Ftimes in Jersey this holiday season.
